## Limitations

The findings are based on general guidelines and may not account for specific individual circumstances. Variations in state laws and personal financial situations can lead to different outcomes. It is advisable for individuals to consult with a financial advisor or legal expert to understand the specific implications of selling a home on their Social Security benefits. Additionally, the information is based on data available up to October 2023, and any changes in laws or regulations after this date are not reflected in this report.